---

The data in this repository is derived from publicly available Contract
Award Notices (Form F03) published in the European Union's Tenders
Electronic Daily (TED), which are themselves released under EU public
sector information directives (Directive (EU) 2019/1024).

The analytical methodology (Tukey IQR outlier detection, 1977) is in
the public domain.
